AUDIO: 'Hey defenders, welcome back. In this video, I\'m going to introduce you guys to the Sock Fortress web application firewall that you can put in front of your application to provide a full self-hosted WAF solution all within 10 minutes. So, stick around and we\'ll jump into it. So, putting a'

[00:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
